overview: Young studs Jaxton Wheeler and Alexander Gustavo know a thing or two about hustling older men for money. Unfortunately, sensitive Tony Salerno doesn't know his relationship with Jaxton isn't the real thing. Meanwhile, gorgeous Billy Santoro craves blue eyed blond escort Alexander's body, but it's Jaxton that really gets his blood boiling. It's hard to tell who's playing who in this emotional, passionate episode of Icon Male's hit series. Starring Jaxton Wheeler, Billy Santoro, Alexander Gustavo, Tony Salerno. Written and directed by Nica Noelle.
tagline: These bad boys need a daddy who can fill all their needs.
title: Sugar Daddies 3
